<Layout title="Contact | Start Your Directory Project" description="Start your directory project with Stackbase System. Share your niche, goals, and scope via async intake.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Start your directory project</h1><p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg">Send your scope asynchronously. I’ll review and reply with a recommended plan and next steps.</p></div></section>
  <section class="py-10"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6"><h2 class="text-xl text-white mb-4">What to include</h2><ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Niche and target audience</li><li>• Current site (if redesign)</li><li>• Needed features (search, filters, auth)</li><li>• Timeline and budget range</li></ul></div><div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6"><h2 class="text-xl text-white mb-4">Contact</h2><p class="text-[#8b8b9a] mb-4">Email: <a class="text-[#00f0ff]" href="mailto:tim@stackbasesystem.com">tim@stackbasesystem.com</a></p><a href="mailto:tim@stackbasesystem.com?subject=New%20Directory%20Project%20Inquiry" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">Email project brief</a></div></div></section>
</Layout>
